[1]
Date: 1 Jun 2011
Source: Orlov News Bureau [Transl. Corr.ATS, edited]
http://www.oryol.ru/material.php?id=22709


Brucellosis reported in the Orlov region
----------------------------------------
The regional veterinary authority has informed about focuses of
animal brucellosis in Krasnozernenski and Zalegoshenski rayons. The
diagnosis has been confirmed in the laboratory. Currently, the
veterinarians are conducting their standard activities for such cases,
particularly destroying all brucellosis positive animals by bloodless
methods, registering all privately owned animals and testing them for
brucellosis. Quarantine is also on place in the affected territories
by the order of the governor.

--
Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

