[3]
Date: 27 May 2011
Source: News portal Ore.Ru [Transl. Corr.ATS, edited]
http://www.oren.ru/news/2591979/http://www.oren.ru/news/2591979/>


Two brucellosis outbreaks in Orenburg
-------------------------------------
The regional authority for veterinary services has announced about 2
focuses of brucellosis in the oblast. One is in the village
Sagarchinski of Akbulakskiy rayon another is in the village Raznomoyka
of Tyulganski rayon. Overall 2 cows and 60 sheep were found infected.
11 people also have been diagnosed with brucellosis. Control measures
are being taken including destruction of the infected herds. The
veterinarians consider that the reason for the infections are non
compliance with veterinarian rules.

--
